# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Digital Signage Kiosk - Complete .gitignore
# Keep only production code, exclude generated/temp/sensitive files
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── Logs & Debugging ─────────────────────────────────────────
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
lerna-debug.log*
report.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.[0-9]*.json

# ─── Runtime & Temp Data ─────────────────────────────────────
pids/
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock
.lock-wscript

# ─── Dependencies ────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
jspm_packages/
web_modules/
bower_components/

# ─── Build Outputs ───────────────────────────────────────────
dist/
.next/
out/
.output/
build/Release/
.parcel-cache/
.cache/
.temp/

# ─── Cache & Build Info ──────────────────────────────────────
*.tsbuildinfo
.nyc_output/
coverage/
*.lcov
.eslintcache
.stylelintcache
.node_repl_history
*.tgz
.yarn-integrity
.svelte-kit/

# ─── Environment & Secrets ───────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.production.local
.env.development.local

# ─── Legacy / Next.js (Deprecated) ───────────────────────────
next-env.d.ts
next.config.ts
middleware.ts
proxy.ts
src/
.zenflow/
.zencoder/
docs-api/
panel/
**/.vercel

# ─── VS Code & IDE ───────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/settings.json
.vscode/launch.json
.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── OS Files ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db

# ─── Runtime Artifacts ───────────────────────────────────────
*.pid.lock
*.sock

# ─── Backup & Database Snapshots ─────────────────────────────
database/backups/**
!database/backups/.gitkeep
database/*.db-shm
database/*.db-wal
*.backup
*.bak

# ─── Generated Documentation ─────────────────────────────────
docs-generated/
api-docs/
typedoc-output/

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ✅ KEEP: Production Code & Essential Files
# ✅ Keep: src-vite/, scripts/, kiosk-agent-cpp/, tests/
# ✅ Keep: prisma/, public/, storage/, database/schema
# ✅ Keep: .github/, docs/, vite.config.ts, package.json
# ✅ Keep: .vscode/extensions.json, launch configs for dev
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# vitepress build output
**/.vitepress/dist

# vitepress cache directory
**/.vitepress/cache

# Docusaurus cache and generated files
.docusaurus

# Serverless directories
.serverless/

# FuseBox cache
.fusebox/

# DynamoDB Local files
.dynamodb/

# Firebase cache directory
.firebase/

# TernJS port file
.tern-port

# Stores VSCode versions used for testing VSCode extensions
.vscode-test

# pnpm
.pnpm-store

# yarn v3
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/sdks
!.yarn/versions

# Vite files
vite.config.js.timestamp-*
vite.config.ts.timestamp-*
.vite/
public/
docs-api/
build/
database/
dist/
.build/
storage/
database/
build/
docs-api/
dist/
.next/